VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bUIApplication\.shared\.open\s*\(|\bUIApplication\.sharedApplication\(\)\.openURL\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:scheme|canOpenURL|allowedSchemes|guard|whitelist|allowlist
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects openURL calls that may open user-controlled or unvalidated URL schemes.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for openURL with Unvalidated Input Scheme.
